. * 2. Constants & Conversions
. * Both cost figures ($3B total, $932M Union loop
> ) treated as 2025 CAD.
. * PPP rate = 0.84, matching World Bank Price Lev
> el Ratio (PA.NUS.PPPC.RF) for
. * Canada: 0.840 in 2024 (most recent available; 
> used as 2025 proxy). This is
. * the same indicator used for all other Canadian
>  projects in this dataset.
. * No inflation adjustment needed since costs are
>  already in 2025 dollars.
. * Source: https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/P
> A.NUS.PPPC.RF?locations=CA
. local total_per_km  = (3000 * 0.84) / 3.8

. local bypass_per_km = (932  * 0.84) / 3.8

. local base_per_km   = `total_per_km' - `bypass_p
> er_km'

. 
